<title>USA: Ocean Reef seeks merger with Jan Bell.</title>
<headline>Ocean Reef seeks merger with Jan Bell.</headline>
<dateline>MIAMI 1996-10-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Ocean Reef Management Inc said on Tuesday that it has proposed a friendly cash merger with Jan Bell Marketing Inc.</p>
<p>No terms of the proposal were released, but Ocean Reef said the merger requires a definitive agreement between the companies, the receipt of satisfactory financing commitments and Jan Bell shareholder approval.  </p>
<p>Jan Bell said the merger would give its shareholders $4.00 per share cash. It said its board would respond to the offer &quot;as promptly as practicable.&quot;</p>
